{
  "description": "A stunning nighttime view of a city skyline, prominently featuring two bridges illuminated with lights. The foreground showcases a modern, cable-stayed bridge with bright white lights outlining its structure and extending across dark water. In the background, a more traditional, older bridge is visible, also lit up but with warmer, yellow tones. The city skyline is a mix of high-rise buildings, creating a dramatic backdrop. Above the cityscape, fireworks explode in a burst of red and white, adding a celebratory and dynamic element to the scene. The overall impression is one of vibrant urban life and a festive atmosphere.",
